thread.title: John Harrington

author: John Harrington
title: John Harrington
text:
We sold a 2011 Toyota Camry LE with 28K miles, WBAC deducted for the cost of detailing it for sale at auction and we left with a check. Craig was friendly and informative through the whole hour long process. It was Mom's car and she was able to wait in our ride home until the final signatures were needed, she never needed to move. Price received was upper end of Edmonds trade, car only had minor scratches to buff out.
All in all, an easy way to sell a car fast.
